  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">supremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Defensive Systems</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit shield strength</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">core health</span>.",
